#. (itstool) path: sect2/para
#: book.translate.xml:14042
msgid ""
"A C compiler has no way of knowing that a value it has on the stack will be "
"required again in the very near future."
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: sect2/para
#: book.translate.xml:14048
msgid ""
